Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:21.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fn微软雅黑\fs38\pos(450,390)\1c&HFFFFFF&}海底两万里 / {\fs18}蓝宝石之谜
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.04,0:00:30.24,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,讨厌懦弱的人 无法背叛蓝天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.31,0:00:36.68,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在做梦之前 我想翱翔天际
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.25,0:00:44.28,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,心中的音乐盒开启 发出声响
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.36,0:00:51.56,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点一滴演奏出幸福与勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.63,0:01:00.27,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在在你眼前 有着无限的未来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.34,0:01:05.78,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,言语是永远的信号
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.85,0:01:10.81,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't forget to try in mind
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:15.72,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,爱比宝石
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.52,0:01:22.93,OP,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,更能照亮一切
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.47,0:01:28.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,距今约一百年前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.74,0:01:31.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,吃下毒菇而昏厥的强
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:34.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚将初吻献给了他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.34,0:01:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,隔天她仿佛变了个人似的 成了一个很乖巧的女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:43.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是在娜蒂亚得知 强完全不记得接吻的事情之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.75,0:01:44.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,为此大发雷霆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强也失去了这个千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.29,0:01:53.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样 他们又在无人岛上 度过安稳祥和的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:58.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但娜蒂亚他们 究竟想在这座岛上待到何时呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.20,0:02:01.83,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,27 魔女所在之岛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.18,0:02:12.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.55,0:02:14.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.22,0:02:18.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.39,0:02:19.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:21.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.62,0:02:24.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是肉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.79,0:02:30.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要是被娜蒂亚听到就糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.60,0:02:35.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是娜蒂亚一定不肯吃
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:39.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题 我有个好主意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.84,0:02:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果用这种卑鄙手段 又会惹她生气喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.88,0:02:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:51.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们的感情好不容易变好了 说不定会因此破局喔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这回保证完美无缺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.29,0:02:57.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚是以味道及口感 来判断肉类
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.09,0:02:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.76,0:03:00.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然她认为自己是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:03.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但在旁人看来不过是偏食罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.83,0:03:08.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是她喜欢吃的紧急粮食 是什么口味的？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:10.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是鲜肉口味
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.94,0:03:11.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.64,0:03:15.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 娜蒂亚讨厌的 是肉的口感
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.98,0:03:18.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以你才要将材料搅拌到 吃不出肉的感觉是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.81,0:03:22.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 我将肉的份量降低了 没问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.88,0:03:25.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用那个可以做出什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.25,0:03:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.39,0:03:28.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.22,0:03:31.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用树的果实的粉做成的皮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.29,0:03:33.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,将馅料包起来再拿去蒸
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这是中国菜
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.80,0:03:37.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 我还是第一次尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.86,0:03:40.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好…好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.23,0:03:42.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也是第一次吃
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.60,0:03:47.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 你会是个好太太
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我是女生的话
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.64,0:03:51.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,配娜蒂亚太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.85,0:03:53.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望会顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.92,0:03:59.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎…怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.99,0:04:03.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,稍微冷掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:04.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好吃吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.83,0:04:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好吃喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.19,0:04:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真…真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.53,0:04:12.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你应该早点做这道菜的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.97,0:04:14.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的？\N真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.07,0:04:21.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,里头该不会有放肉吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.84,0:04:23.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我才不会做那种事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.52,0:04:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你怎么了？强
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:35.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果…我还是骗了她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.52,0:04:37.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,她知情了才算欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:42.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果她不知情就不算欺骗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:45.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但我总觉得心里不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.03,0:04:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,堂堂男子汉 是不会为过去感到后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.27,0:04:52.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你要更坚强才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:56.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这些话是谁教你的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.84,0:04:58.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.28,0:05:03.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你有打算要跟娜蒂亚结婚吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.08,0:05:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我也不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.68,0:05:07.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 结婚…结婚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.99,0:05:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结婚也不错喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.76,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想早点结婚\N嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.46,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这可是所有女孩的梦想\N说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:16.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我希望能在29岁前结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.06,0:05:20.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我想在26岁前结婚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.97,0:05:24.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这种事还是愈早愈好
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.24,0:05:27.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,像在勒阿弗尔的蕾伊 就已经结婚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.08,0:05:32.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 在这里也没办法结婚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.85,0:05:34.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,既没有教堂也没有区公所
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:38.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你们可以先订婚啊\N订婚？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.32,0:05:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,订婚这个主意不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.02,0:05:41.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 戒指也没有着落啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.96,0:05:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,提到没有着落
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.39,0:05:45.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今天的晚餐不也是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.33,0:05:47.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.53,0:05:51.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,比起订婚 还不如多操心今晚的食物 (『订婚』音近『今晚的食物』)
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.43,0:05:54.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说到底 你不过是个傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.30,0:05:56.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.07,0:05:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说到底 我不过是个傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.34,0:06:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉好想早点到其它地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:04.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:05.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真想早点离开那座小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.85,0:06:08.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,到有教堂及区公所的地方去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:11.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉今天好想吃鱼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.99,0:06:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我已经吃腻乌贼和章鱼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.82,0:06:18.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,乌贼和章鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.69,0:06:19.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,章鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.49,0:06:23.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.30,0:06:25.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？\N那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:27.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风筝啊 (『章鱼』音同『风筝』)
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:29.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,风筝？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.74,0:06:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就用这个飞上天 离开这座小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是看它的大小 根本载不了三个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.04,0:06:40.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,首先要从侦查开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,先派一个人乘着这个风筝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:44.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,调查这座岛的周边环境
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.79,0:06:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那要派谁去？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.59,0:06:50.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.94,0:07:04.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.97,0:07:06.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,然后要怎么做？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.27,0:07:12.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,观测风向 风速 水平线还有测定距离
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.28,0:07:15.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,由大王来做这些吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.45,0:07:16.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.97,0:07:43.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我完全忘了大王是动物
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.84,0:07:46.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:47.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是乌云
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:53.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望远镜…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.49,0:08:00.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只要是你制作的东西 每个都会往下掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.36,0:08:01.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.59,0:08:03.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟都违反地心引力嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.90,0:08:06.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不能降落得更帅气一点吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.27,0:08:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要飞起来就很不容易了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我根本没空顾虑降落的事\N大王…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.57,0:08:10.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:12.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真是拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:13.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.51,0:08:16.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,望远镜的镜头可能会破掉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王要是受伤怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.91,0:08:20.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,受伤能够痊愈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.25,0:08:22.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但破掉的镜头可就无法复原
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.48,0:08:25.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你的意思是 镜头比大王还重要啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:26.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我又没那么说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你明明就是这个意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.35,0:08:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:34.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王\N镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.00,0:08:38.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.83,0:08:40.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,幸好你没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.70,0:08:42.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.54,0:08:44.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是指什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王…平安没事太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.32,0:09:00.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 大王说有台风正朝这里逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.55,0:09:01.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.45,0:09:04.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以风筝才会被强风吹落
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.32,0:09:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:08.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有台风正朝着这座小岛逼近
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.19,0:09:34.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 没问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:37.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大概？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟我以前从未见过台风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.44,0:09:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.98,0:10:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好强的风
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.98,0:10:03.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是台风啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.28,0:10:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的没问题吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.62,0:10:11.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,墙壁全都补强过了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,缝隙也全都塞住了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.29,0:10:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,入口也做了双重防护 绝对不会有问题的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.06,0:10:18.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天花板呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.13,0:10:20.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天花板？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,天花板啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.74,0:10:27.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么都没做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.27,0:10:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？\N你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.91,0:10:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:34.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.35,0:10:35.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.63,0:10:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,花了好几个月 才建立起来的科学文明
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.43,0:10:57.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过是经历台风一晚的摧残
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.90,0:10:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就什么都不剩了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.77,0:11:01.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就是大自然的威力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.12,0:11:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王是被吹到哪里去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:16.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,找了那么久都没找到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.56,0:11:18.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,今晚就先放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.26,0:11:20.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,等天亮了再重新找一遍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.99,0:11:23.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.43,0:11:25.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,抱歉 娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果我把那间小屋 盖得更坚固的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.14,0:11:32.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这并不是你的错
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.10,0:11:33.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.41,0:11:35.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你已经尽力了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.91,0:11:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,别再自责了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.38,0:11:45.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定会有好事发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.62,0:11:47.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.75,0:11:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,有流星
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.29,0:11:53.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,据说向流星许愿 愿望就会实现喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.06,0:11:59.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你许了什么愿望？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.43,0:12:01.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望能早点找到大王
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.93,0:12:03.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.70,0:12:04.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,希望能早点离开这座小岛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.98,0:12:10.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只有这些？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:13.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:15.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.41,0:12:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那个是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.69,0:12:22.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,山在动？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.22,0:12:24.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不对 那应该是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.39,0:12:25.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:48.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这果然不是梦或是幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会是海市蜃楼吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海市蜃楼不会那么清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:56.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,顺着台风漂过来的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.16,0:12:58.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会有这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.72,0:13:00.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是大陆飘移学说
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.66,0:13:02.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大陆飘移学说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.46,0:13:04.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前尼莫船长不是说过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.86,0:13:08.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,地球上的大陆原本都是同一块
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.43,0:13:12.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是经由长年累月 才移动到现在的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:17.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是那座岛才一个晚上 就突然出现在我们面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.44,0:13:22.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一定是因为地壳变动 海底突然隆起而形成岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:25.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真有这种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.45,0:13:32.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这地球可以说是个 超乎我们想像的大型生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:33.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然大陆沉入海中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.76,0:13:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有像这样 一个晚上就形成岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.00,0:13:39.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对人类来说或许是件大事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:40.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但从地球的角度来看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.43,0:13:42.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这不过是件小事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.10,0:13:47.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人类真是种渺小的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错 地球是会动的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.91,0:13:51.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 是有生命的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.58,0:13:52.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.31,0:13:54.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.28,0:13:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王在那边 那边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.82,0:14:04.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是大王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.03,0:14:15.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.53,0:14:17.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.44,0:14:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这下子我们就用不着担心 水和食物了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:23.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 照这情况来看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.08,0:14:25.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这并不像是 才刚出现一两天的岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.52,0:14:33.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王说另一头有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.65,0:14:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王说…玛莉你…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.62,0:14:38.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你听得懂大王在说什么吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.06,0:14:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 因为我们两情相悦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.23,0:14:44.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我过去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:46.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.40,0:14:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得那里会有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.03,0:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不要紧的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:53.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我马上就会回来的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:54.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.71,0:15:02.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,大王刚才是用两只脚跑掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.85,0:15:03.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最近总觉得不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.35,0:15:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然不对劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.62,0:15:14.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才一个晚上就突然出现的岛屿 怎么可能会不奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:17.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你看看那些树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.13,0:15:22.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这边的树与生长在对面的树 品种完全不同
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.30,0:15:28.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我记得那应该是 生长在寒带的针叶树
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.51,0:15:29.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你再往那边看看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.91,0:15:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那一头似乎还看得到沙漠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:33.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:37.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 那看来像是沙丘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.68,0:15:40.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛一定有问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:42.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你是怎么了？娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.76,0:15:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一点都不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:46.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你平常明明都会否定到底的说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.29,0:15:49.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我有种不舒服的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也不晓得为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.00,0:15:55.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总觉得这座岛上 一定存在着什么秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:58.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强 我们快点回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.54,0:16:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也对 那我去叫玛莉和大王
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.78,0:16:07.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉 回岛上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.65,0:16:10.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里太诡异了 我们还是回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.08,0:16:13.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里有个人头人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.39,0:16:14.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人头人？\N人头人？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.60,0:16:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我的天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.50,0:16:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太狠毒了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.43,0:16:28.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,原来岛上有居民
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.90,0:16:30.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这里有人住？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.50,0:16:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,活跃于16世纪的探险家麦哲伦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.81,0:16:35.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在环绕世界一周的航行途中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.31,0:16:37.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,曾在登陆的岛上 遭岛上居民攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.25,0:16:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,现在还会发生那种事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:43.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,错不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.62,0:16:46.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这个人一定是成了对方的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.99,0:16:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚 这座岛果然危险
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.39,0:16:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,快点回去吧\N好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.09,0:16:52.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.66,0:16:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,人头人还活着耶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.26,0:16:56.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你说什么？\N你说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:03.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放…放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.57,0:17:06.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我愿意为你们做牛做马
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.67,0:17:08.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以拜托你们救救我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.97,0:17:10.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他说话了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.48,0:17:12.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他是被活埋的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.38,0:17:15.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,求求你们 千错万错都是我的错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.45,0:17:16.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,放过我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:20.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没事了 我马上就救你出来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.79,0:17:22.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.45,0:17:25.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对了 冒昧再请问一句
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.16,0:17:27.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你身上有水吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.99,0:17:30.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就是水啊 水
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.96,0:17:32.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,咦？\N咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.20,0:17:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿先生
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.84,0:17:41.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿先生 从刚才就一直喝水喝个不停
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.31,0:17:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好喝 这才是自然原味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就像吸墨纸似的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.51,0:17:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我没吃没喝很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.28,0:17:55.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不过 这些天然涌泉中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:58.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,含有许多浮游生物及微生物
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.39,0:18:03.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,长时间持续饮用会导致中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.46,0:18:05.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,听起来真不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:07.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是说真的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.63,0:18:11.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟我可是个微生物专家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.67,0:18:14.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不说那个了 你在这里做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.81,0:18:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.18,0:18:19.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这就要提到一段 很长的前情提要了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.68,0:18:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,本人 艾尔顿·葛雷纳邦伯爵
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:26.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接受美国海军的委托
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.59,0:18:30.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,率领海兽扫荡舰队 执行作战行动的某天晚上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:34.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你不是海洋学家吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.66,0:18:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对外是那么宣称的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:41.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,毕竟连美国海军 都不晓得我的真正身分
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.37,0:18:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 那天夜里
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:46.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我终于发现神秘大海兽 并加以追踪
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这件事我们也晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.94,0:18:52.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,因为我与娜蒂亚 当时也在战舰上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:55.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你真的记得我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.95,0:18:57.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,当然记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:00.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃…你叫什么名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.22,0:19:02.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.06,0:19:04.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我叫强
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.66,0:19:07.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对对 我刚想起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.86,0:19:08.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,强与巴德
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:09.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,娜蒂亚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.83,0:19:10.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我是玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.06,0:19:13.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没错没错 娜蒂亚还有玛莉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.40,0:19:14.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我都记得喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.07,0:19:17.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉真的长大了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.10,0:19:20.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之前见面时 你还这么小一个
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:24.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉从没见过这位叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,总之 后来我们对大海兽 发动总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.25,0:19:31.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果却被海兽打得落花流水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.18,0:19:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们就是在那个时候掉进海里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.35,0:19:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那你们应该不清楚 后来发生什么事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.46,0:19:41.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那只海兽其实是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.86,0:19:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,世界第一艘实用潜水艇\N世界第一艘实用潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.76,0:19:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你…你们怎么会知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.23,0:19:49.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那是军方的重要机密耶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.70,0:19:53.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,艾尔顿先生 更惊人的东西我们都见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.04,0:19:56.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以请你说实话好吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.54,0:19:59.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,OK 那好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,接下来我说的都是实话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:03.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们失踪之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.75,0:20:06.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们再度遇上那艘潜水艇
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.02,0:20:09.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,战舰对它发动总攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.92,0:20:12.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在攻击的冲击下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.96,0:20:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我掉到了海中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.40,0:20:21.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然幸运地保住小命
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.60,0:20:23.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但是却找不到舰队
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.50,0:20:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,只好抱着附近装了粮食的木桶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.57,0:20:33.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,漂流了好几天
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.18,0:20:36.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后漂流到这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.52,0:20:40.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就这样而已吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.75,0:20:43.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不 辛苦的在那之后才开始
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.96,0:20:48.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,在这座岛上发生的事 全都非常不可思议
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.79,0:20:51.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太阳从西方升起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.23,0:20:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一整天都是夜晚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.10,0:20:57.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,会结出热带水果 却也会下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,才想说连续好几天都是大太阳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.37,0:21:02.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,结果却发现海面竟然结冰了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.98,0:21:06.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.15,0:21:07.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:11.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,如果要撒谎 我会说得更高明的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.38,0:21:16.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有 这座岛上的重力也不太正常
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.32,0:21:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,让人能跑得异常快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.66,0:21:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还能跳得异常高
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.93,0:21:24.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不光是那样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.00,0:21:28.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,形状吓人的岩石
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.10,0:21:31.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从洞穴深处传出的啜泣声
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.07,0:21:32.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,一到夜晚就会发光的海面
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.87,0:21:35.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,莫名其妙消失的粮食
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.67,0:21:39.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛上没有半件事是正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.65,0:21:45.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,这座岛果然存在着某些秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.35,0:21:50.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,玛莉肚子快饿扁了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.69,0:21:52.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,不晓得还会发生什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.39,0:21:54.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们快回林肯岛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.46,0:21:55.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们先别走
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.43,0:21:58.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我话还没说完
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:01.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,重要的部分现在才要开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,从现在算起约一个月前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.54,0:22:09.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐怖大王出现在这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.58,0:22:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐怖大王？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.21,0:22:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,对
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.21,0:22:16.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,用恐怖大王来形容那些家伙 可说是实至名归
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.15,0:22:22.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第一只是红发大嗓门魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.19,0:22:23.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,第二只是身材消瘦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.63,0:22:30.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,却是个超级大力士 而且长得很高的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.23,0:22:32.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,超级大力士？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:37.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,最后一只则是 圆滚滚胖嘟嘟的魔物
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.14,0:22:39.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,胖嘟嘟的魔物？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.74,0:22:45.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,还有一只负责载运那些家伙 以四只脚行走的恶魔手下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.18,0:22:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恶魔手下？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.98,0:22:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,自从被那些恐怖大王抓住之后
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.18,0:22:54.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我就生活在地狱之中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,他们所谓的奖赏
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.52,0:23:02.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然是强迫我吃他们所吃的 如同熔岩般滚烫的食物
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.70,0:23:04.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,太过份了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.06,0:23:07.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,简直就是人间地狱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.37,0:23:09.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就算趁隙脱逃
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.64,0:23:11.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但毕竟还是在这座岛上
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.20,0:23:13.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,所以不一会就被找到
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.31,0:23:16.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,之后的下场你们也见过了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.07,0:23:21.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,也就是说 那些恐怖大王 随时都有可能出现啰？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.85,0:23:24.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我们还是快回岛上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.45,0:23:26.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,好 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:29.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,你们会带我一起走对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.15,0:23:32.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,嗯 不过你要负责划船喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.72,0:23:35.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,那点小事不成问题
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:37.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么声音？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.90,0:23:45.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.47,0:23:46.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出…\N出…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.47,0:23:48.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,出现了！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.44,0:23:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,恐怖大王
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.28,0:23:54.84,Title,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,待续
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.91,0:24:02.82,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,该怎么应付心中的焦急才好？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.89,0:24:07.95,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,就要看不清远方的梦想了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.03,0:24:12.36,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我喃喃自语 仰望星空
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.43,0:24:21.31,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与你的约定耀眼闪烁着
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.37,0:24:31.41,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try 安慰的话语 是传达不到内心的风
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.48,0:24:40.19,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,虽然背负的不安逐渐膨胀
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.26,0:24:44.46,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,但这是我自己的决定
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.53,0:24:49.09,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,我一个人应该也不要紧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.17,0:24:58.17,ED,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,即使跌倒或感到迷惘 仍然有明天
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.82,0:25:09.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,完全不在乎会为他人带来困扰
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.76,0:25:12.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝军团驾到
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.16,0:25:14.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,葛兰迪丝 还有桑森与韩森
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.99,0:25:15.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.89,0:25:17.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,竟然把我当成魔女？
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.56,0:25:18.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,没大脑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.03,0:25:21.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,与让人怀念的葛兰迪丝他们 重逢的这座岛居然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.87,0:25:25.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,举世罕见的怪异岛屿
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.27,0:25:30.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,海底两万里 下一回 『漂流岛』
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.14,0:25:31.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,要看喔\N要看喔
